  initialDialog:
  - You're finally awake. You've been out cold for two whole days.
  - I found you passed out deep in the forest. Lucky I dragged you back here before
    the wolves caught your scent.
  - But I can't protect you forever. You need to defend yourself. Gather 5 Wood and
    3 Stone nearby, and I'll help you craft an Axe.
